   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cancer program for kids to detect cancer early</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our cancer school programme educates students about the importance of detecting cancer early and how to support cancer patients in their communities. Education is the best weapon against cancer, which lacks due to the diverse society in South Africa, where cultural taboos, stigmas and a lack of knowledge about the subject is plentiful. One student&apos;s educational goodie bag is likely to reach 7 others due to the household situation in South Africa. We educate about cancer for US$ 1.10 per student.</narrative>
  </description>
